# Brain build ignore. Context = services/brain (self-contained; app/pb is
# committed, so no repo-root proto tree is pulled in). These rules keep the
# build context — and therefore the image — free of dev-only artifacts. The
# Dockerfile also COPYs only pyproject.toml + app/, never the items below.
.venv
venv
**/__pycache__
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache
tests
dist
build
*.egg-info
.env
.env.*
*.log
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
